                               int intWhereType,
                               java.util.Vector vtFields,
                               ChannelRuntimeData runtimeData)
                        throws neuragenix.dao.exception.DAOQueryInvalidField
Sets the where clause for multiple fields

Parameters:
strInitialConnector - Connector for the first field in the set
strGroupConnector - Connector for field_2 to field_n
intOpenBrackets - Open brackets will start for the first field only
intCloseBrackets - Close brackets are applied to the last field
intWhereType - Where type is constant for all fields
vtFields - Form fields that the function should be interested in
runtimeData - Channel runtime data for the fields
Throws:
neuragenix.dao.exception.DAOQueryInvalidField

strInitialConnector - Connector for the first field in the set

strAOperator - Operator that will be applied to all fields
intOpenBrackets - Open brackets will start for the first field only
intCloseBrackets - Close brackets are applied to the last field
intWhereType - Where type is constant for all fields
